show.description: Ellie Scott’s world shatters when her husband, Dr. Zack Scott, gives their son’s heart to his ex-lover Raichel’s son, leading to Howie’s death. Devastated, Ellie fights for justice, causing Zack to confront his mistake and make a final sacrifice to save her. In the end, Rachel is exposed and imprisoned, while Ellie’s grief gives way to redemption.
